tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE UserBehavior (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    event_type VARCHAR(50),
    action_taken VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE UserSessions (
  session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  start_time TIMESTAMP,
  end_time TIMESTAMP,
  duration INT
);

CREATE TABLE analytics_table (
    analytics_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    event_id INT NOT NULL,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    action_id INT NOT NULL,
    analytics_data JSONB
);
CREATE TABLE user_accounts (user_id INT PRIMARY KEY, username VARCHAR(50), email VARCHAR(100), created_at TIMESTAMP);
CREATE TABLE user_activity (activity_id INT PRIMARY KEY, user_id INT, activity_type VARCHAR(50), activity_description TEXT, activity_timestamp TIMESTAMP);
CREATE TABLE page_views (page_id INT PRIMARY KEY, page_name VARCHAR(100), user_id INT, timestamp TIMESTAMP);
CREATE TABLE user_devices (device_id INT PRIMARY KEY, user_id INT, device_type VARCHAR(50), device_model VARCHAR(50), last_used TIMESTAMP);
CREATE TABLE user_preferences (preference_id INT PRIMARY KEY, user_id INT, preference_name VARCHAR(50), preference_value TEXT);
